<h1>HGV accident repairs and painting, North West and Wirral</h1>
<p>If your vehicle is damaged in an accident, we&#8217;ll take care of the repair process from start to finish. We&#8217;re the only commercial vehicle body shop in the North Wales, the North West, and Wirral equipped to deal with the heaviest commercial vehicle accidents.</p>
</div>

<div>
<h2>Any commercial vehicle</h2>

<p>We use the latest Josam cab and chassis repair equipment, computerised paint schemes and low-bake commercial ovens to ensure vehicles are returned to pre-accident condition. Our sign writers can replicate original graphics for your vehicles.</p>
</div>

<div>
<h2>Our HGV accident repairs and painting workshop</h2>

<ul class="list--plain">
<li>60' Josam chassis frame alignment jig</li>
<li>Josam heat inductor</li>
<li>2 x Josam cab repair benches</li>
<li>Korek floor-mounted, heavy-duty jig system</li>
<li>Laser measuring for multi-axle vehicles</li>
<li>Tig, mig, spot, and aluminium welding</li>
<li>Steel sheet and aluminium fabrication</li>
</ul>
</div>

<div>
<h2>Insurance work</h2>

<p>We&#8217;ll liaise with you, your fleet engineers, and the insurance/accident management company to make sure the repair process flows smoothly from start to finish. We&#8217;ll arrange collection of a damaged vehicle and return it repaired and ready to work.</p>
